high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the white table, turn right, go straight to the black stand.
Take the knife from the stand.
Turn right, go straight to the wall, turn right,  go straight to the white table.
Cut the apple on the table into pieces.
Turn right, go straight and to the left to the oven.
Put the knife in the pot on the left on the stove top.
Turn around, go straight to the wall, turn right to face the white table.
Take a piece of the cut apple.
Turn right, go straight and to the left to the oven.
Put the apple in the pot on the left on the stove top.
Take the left pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go straight, when the fridge is to the left turn left towards the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the pot on the top shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a piece of apple in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, turn right towards a table with two salt shakers and two tomatoes.
Pick up a knife from the table near the left tomato and salt shaker..
Turn right, carry the knife around the fridge, turn right again and walk toward the table.
Cut he piece of food next to the salt shaker on the table.
Turn right and carry the knife to the stove.
Set the knife in the left pan on the stove.
Turn around and walk back to the table where the food was cut.
Pick up a piece of the cut food.
Turn right and carry the food to the stove.
Drop the food in the pan with the knife.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around, carry the pan across the room, then turn right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with food in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the end table with two tomatoes on it at the end of the counter.
Pick up the butter knife on the table.
Go to the table in the corner with the microwave on it.
Slice the apple next to the salt shaker.
Turn and walk past the table on the left to the stove.
Put the knife into the pan on the  left of the stove.
Go back to the table with the microwave on it.
Pick up a slice of apple next to the salt shaker.
Turn and walk past the table on the left to the stove.
Put the apple in the pan with the butter knife.
Pick up the pan with the butter knife and apple slice in it.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Put the pan with the butter knife and apple slice into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan, with an apple slice next to a butter knife inside, into the fridge.
